Kwaviya yelihi yoyamanya magesa ya munhu, ila Muhe wa Mulungu yeli mgati mmwake? Iviya habule munhu yoyamanya magesa ya Mulungu ila Muhe wa Mulungu muhala.
Mbali cheye hachihokela Muhe wa isi ino bule, mbali chihokela Muhe yoyalawile kwa Mulungu, muladi chimanye vinhu viya viya Mulungu vovichipatile.
