Kwaviya fana imwe kolonga, "Niye wa Paulo," na imwenga, "Niye wa Apolo," vino mweye siyo wanhu fana mweye?
Apolo ni yelihi? Paulo ni yelihi? Ni wasang'hani muhala womuihuwile mweye, fana Mndewa viyamwing'hile chila munhu sang'hano yake.
