Ivo munhu yohanda mbeyu na munhu yotenda mazi siyo chinhu, mbali Mulungu yaidumwe iyo yoitenda ikule.
Munhu yoyohanda mbeyu na munhu yoyoing'ha mazi viya viya imwe. Chila munhu kezahokela gweko jake fana viyatendile.
Kwaviya cheye cha wasang'hani wayage na Mulungu. Mweye mwa mgunda wa Mulungu, na mweye mwa kaye ya Mulungu.
Ivo kwa unovu wa Mulungu, yoyaninile, niye nizenga chandusilo fana munhu yoyazengile kuzengela, na munhu imwenga kazengela mchanyha yake. Mbali chila munhu kolondeka yailole viya viyazengile.
Kwaviya habule munhu yoyose yoyodaha kuzenga chandusilo chimwenga mbali chiya chizengigwe kamala, icho ni Yesu Chilisito.
