Kwaviya ubala wa isi ino ni ubozi kwa Mulungu. Kwaviya Yamaandiko Yelile yolonga, "Mulungu kowagwila weli na ubala muna ubala wawo."
Maabaho yandika kaidi, "Mndewa kovimanya magesa ya wanhu weli na ubala kuwa yabule faida."
Ivo munhu yoyose sekeyeve mbuli za wanhu, kwaviya chila chinhu ni chenu.
